{"tid":1762913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【11.18•油麻地人疊人】CCTV曝光證警驅急救員　人堆後射胡椒劑","createTime":"2019-11-30T02:46:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T09:33:27.000Z","uid":78222,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"1eb89546e847aa5801e7dc89e35dae5a93784cd0","tid":1762913,"uid":78222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:46:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">入面有片，自己睇</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/403296/11-18-%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8A%E4%BA%BA-cctv%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%AD%89%E8%AD%A6%E9%A9%85%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%93%A1-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%86%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%8A%91\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F01%25E5%2581%25B5%25E6%259F%25A5%2F403296%2F11-18-%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E9%25BA%25BB%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2596%258A%25E4%25BA%25BA-cctv%25E6%259B%259D%25E5%2585%2589%25E8%25AD%2589%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%25A9%2585%25E6%2580%25A5%25E6%2595%2591%25E5%2593%25A1-%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A0%2586%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%25B0%2584%25E8%2583%25A1%25E6%25A4%2592%25E5%258A%2591&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYxZ9qy%2BOiqBAJcOKDokr%2FlY%3D&h=da2967d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%81%B5%E6%9F%A5/403296/11-18-%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%96%8A%E4%BA%BA-cctv%E6%9B%9D%E5%85%89%E8%AD%89%E8%AD%A6%E9%A9%85%E6%80%A5%E6%95%91%E5%93%A1-%E4%BA%BA%E5%A0%86%E5%BE%8C%E5%B0%84%E8%83%A1%E6%A4%92%E5%8A%91</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><ins>個人認為重點係</ins></span><br />\n一：<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">警方否認人踩人</span></span><br />\n二：證實當晚有警員驅趕急救員及記者離開。<br />\n<br />\n自己睇完條片，入面有消防員出黎休息個樣係勁灰，有機會係被狗趕走而唔係攰<br />\n<br />\ncopy左幾段，手機唔方便<br />\n--------------------------文章------------------------<br />\n上周一（18日）夜晚，大批黑衣人到油尖旺一帶聲援理工大學內的示威者，警方沿彌敦道向旺角方向驅散，在油麻地碧街附近拘捕213人，期間有逾30人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n警方事後否認碧街曾發生「人踩人」，不過有現場相片顯示黑衣人堆疊。本周一（25日），有義務急救員公開指責，有警員當晚眼見發生「人疊人」，仍阻礙消防員及急救員救援。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》取得兩段碧街閉路電視，證實當晚有警員驅趕急救員及記者離開。另一網上片段顯示，有警員不但未即時疏導人堆，反在人堆後方噴射胡椒噴劑。<br />\n<br />\n警方今日（29日）指，難辨認義務急救員身份，有需要將他們排除在封鎖線外。立法會議員毛孟靜批評，驅趕急救員罔顧被困者安全，促警方進一步解釋。"},{"pid":"5d22d8051c5e64b91d350cd4d4ee2e5a7965d5c9","tid":1762913,"uid":78222,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:47:52.000Z","msg":"23:28-23:30　社媒拍攝到人疊人　警員驅趕義務急救員離開小巷<br />\n<br />\n23:28，八名身穿反光衣的急救員及一名記者離開小巷，其中一人曾跌倒由其他人扶起，眾人再被警員驅趕離開。一分鐘後，畫面顯示警員再分別驅趕一名記者及一名義務急救員離開。<br />\n<br />\n23:29，《United Social Press社媒》的攝影記者在A1出口外拍攝，相片顯示小巷內有數十名黑衣人堆疊在一起，至少兩名消防員及兩名義務急救員協助救援，拉起被困的人。<br />\n<br />\n23:30，商店A閉路電視畫面顯示，四名消防員離開小巷。<br />\n<br />\n23:33　小巷外碧街馬路　<span style=\"color: red;\">兩消防員脫面罩休息　一人曾跪地</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSawPqi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSawPqi.jpg&h=4a92378c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df0c280ff013bdaf971730abdf8d6270947c344e","tid":1762913,"uid":308163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"推吓"},{"pid":"b40208a2f3350c943f10bced3a33f7d696a58223","tid":1762913,"uid":214635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"01真係咁撚夠薑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"5d74000a37d4aadb75292d3cda603f30dd30bdd5","tid":1762913,"uid":260296,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:49:26.000Z","msg":"又比人大事化小<br />\n<br />\n幫手推啦"},{"pid":"538fa522d17e6fc2c76e8744d5d4e65aeaa7f857","tid":1762913,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:52:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9783ce334e05fda0956130a40aeb751e14c60b1","tid":1762913,"uid":199739,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T02:52:22.0